PN,34401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FFormer Sheffield United footballer
OL,8,FMaddy Cusack from Derby was "dismayed"
OL,9,Fthat her previous coach was joining
OL,10,Fher club months before she died, her
OL,11,Ffather told an inquest.
OL,13,FMaddy died aged 27 and was found at
OL,14,Fher home address in Horsley in
OL,15,FDerbyshire, on September 20th, 2023.
OL,26,@pD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FLess than a week after Maddy's death,
OL,8,Fher family sent a written complaint to
OL,9,FSheffield United alleging she had been
OL,10,Ffacing issues arising from her
OL,11,Frelationship with the team's head
OL,12,Fcoach at the time, Jonathan Morgan.
OL,14,FThe club subsequently investigated
OL,15,Fand, in December 2023, announced it
OL,16,Fhad found no evidence of wrongdoing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FIn November of that year, the Maddy
OL,8,FCusack Foundation, which was created
OL,9,Fin her memory, shared a speech online
OL,10,Fattributed to Ms Cusack's mother which
OL,11,Fsaid the player's spirit "was allowed
OL,12,Fto be broken" by football.
OL,14,FChesterfield Coroner's Court heard
OL,15,Ftoday (June 29th) how Maddy feared
OL,16,Fbeing stigmatised and ridiculed at the
OL,17,Fclub.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FThe court was also told that Maddy was
OL,8,F"so happy" to leave Leicester City,
OL,9,Fwhere she had first worked with Mr
OL,10,FMorgan, and was "loving life" until he
OL,11,Fbecame her coach again at Sheffield
OL,12,FUnited in February 2023.
OL,14,FHer father, David Cusack, said she
OL,15,Fthen "fell on her feet" when she
OL,16,Fjoined the South Yorkshire club in
OL,17,FJanuary 2019, where she also started
OL,18,Fworking for Sheffield United's
OL,19,Fmarketing team part-time.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]rD@QOUrD@]O]wD@FOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "(She was) dismayed by the
OL,8,Fpossibility of him coming back into
OL,9,Fher life. I'm going to say 'look, it
OL,10,Fmay have changed. It's a fresh start
OL,11,Ffor both of you'. I tried to be
OL,12,Fpositive".
OL,14,FThe inquest heard that Maddy stopped
OL,15,Fbeing so strict about her healthy diet
OL,16,Fbefore her death, with her father
OL,17,Fadding: "I think, towards the end, she
OL,18,Fwas demotivated.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@IO]yD@IOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,F"She didn't let herself go, or
OL,8,Fanything like that. She was
OL,9,Fdemotivated or deflated."
OL,11,FMr Morgan, who is representing himself
OL,12,Fin the inquest, asked Mr Cusack if he
OL,13,Fwas aware that his daughter left
OL,14,FLeicester City because she sustained a
OL,15,Fhamstring injury that limited her
OL,16,Fplaying time.
OL,18,FMr Cusack said he thought his daughter
OL,19,Fhad not played matches at Leicester
OL,20,Fbecause of a "clash of personalities".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@YO]|D@NOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe also told the inquest that the
OL,8,F"worst thing that could have happened"
OL,9,Fbefore Maddy's death was "the one
OL,10,Fthing she wanted" ` signing a contract
OL,11,Fto play football full-time at
OL,12,FSheffield United.
OL,14,FBy the summer of 2023, Mr Cusack said,
OL,15,Fhis daughter was "fretting" about her
OL,16,Fclub contract.
OL,18,FHe said: "We knew she was not very
OL,19,Fhappy about how things had gone. She
OL,20,Fbecame unwell in July. I think that
OL,21,Fwas as a result of the contract.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@fO]qD@ZOUrD@QO]wD@ROUwD@[O]zD@
OL,26,AJOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,F"It was strung out most of the summer,
OL,8,Fthat contract.
OL,10,F"My own theory about that was it was a
OL,11,Fcase of 'if we don't offer her a
OL,12,Fcontract she will look somewhere
OL,13,Felse'."
OL,15,FHe told the inquest that when Maddy
OL,16,Fsigned to become a full-time player,
OL,17,Fshe found it difficult because
OL,18,Ftraining hours clashed with her
OL,19,Fmarketing job.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FHe said: "She was anxious, worried,
OL,8,Fhow she was going to be able to
OL,9,Fcombine the two roles. The money was
OL,10,Fless than it was the previous year.
OL,11,FShe just lost her joie de vivre."
OL,13,FAsked about a comment by Maddy that
OL,14,Fshe had "no future", her father said:
OL,15,F"She's got to give up something. She
OL,16,Fcouldn't carry on like this. We
OL,17,Fthought she was depressed, not
OL,18,Fsuicidal."
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@aO]vD@IOUvD@SO]wD@AOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FThe inquest heard that Sheffield
OL,8,FUnited did not offer any psychotherapy
OL,9,For other support to Maddy, and she was
OL,10,Fgiven a sick note for time off work by
OL,11,Fa doctor.
OL,13,FMr Cusack said that his daughter, who
OL,14,Fwas prescribed medication, felt that
OL,15,Fif she used her mental health as an
OL,16,F"excuse" she "would be out" of the
OL,17,Fteam, and feared being stigmatised and
OL,18,Fridiculed.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@HO]xD@NOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FMr Cusack added: "It wouldn't be the
OL,8,Ffirst time an organisation stigmatised
OL,9,Fsomeone not well enough to work."
OL,11,FThe father told the court he found his
OL,12,Fdaughter upstairs in their family home
OL,13,Fon the evening of her death with
OL,14,Fligature marks around her neck before
OL,15,Fhe attempted CPR and called for an
OL,16,Fambulance.
OL,18,FMr Cusack told the inquest: "After she
OL,19,Fpassed away, we wanted ` and still
OL,20,Fwant ` those we think are responsible
OL,21,Fto be held responsible.
OL,26,@oD@ROUqD@aO]zD@]OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,F"Rather than just let it go, 'what a
OL,8,Fshame', I decided I wanted to write
OL,9,Fdown what her problems were, what she
OL,10,Ftold us her problems were, and make a
OL,11,Fcomplaint.
OL,13,F"The man in the firing line was Mr
OL,14,FMorgan.
OL,16,F"I wanted to air the grievances we had.
OL,18,F"This is no mystery, it's all there."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOUzD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FMr Cusack said his daughter was
OL,8,F"talented at most sports" but
OL,9,F"football was her passion".
OL,11,FThe Football Association began its own
OL,12,Finvestigation in January 2024, with
OL,13,Fthe governing body saying at the time
OL,14,Fthat its purpose was "to understand
OL,15,Fwhether or not any further action is
OL,16,Frequired under our jurisdiction within
OL,17,Ffootball".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@YO]qD@AOUqD@ZO]vD@VOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FThe FA report was shared with the
OL,8,Fcoroner a year later, but it will not
OL,9,Fbe published until the inquest has
OL,10,Fconcluded.
OL,12,FThe inquest, which is being heard at
OL,13,FChesterfield Coroner's Court, was
OL,14,Fpreviously postponed because of delays
OL,15,Fin disclosure of information to Ms
OL,16,FCusack's family.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1782778699
OL,3,CMaddy Cusack 'dismayed' before death
OL,4,Cwhen previous coach joined Sheffield
OL,5,CUnited
OL,7,FMr Morgan was sacked by Sheffield
OL,8,FUnited in February 2024 after
OL,9,Finformation came to light about a
OL,10,Frelationship he had with a player
OL,11,Fwhile he was in charge at Leicester
OL,12,FCity.
OL,14,FSheffield United's own investigation,
OL,15,Fwhich concluded in December 2023,
OL,16,Ffound no evidence of wrongdoing.
OL,18,FHis dismissal was not related to the
OL,19,FFA investigation.
OL,21,FThe inquest continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/15
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
